name: Wrapped Elephant
description: Elephant Money is a DeFi ecosystem built around two core tokens: ELEPHANT, a fixed supply asset on BNB Chain, and WELEPHANT, its wrapped version deployed on Base for cross-chain utility. ELEPHANT is designed for long-term value through strategic supply compression and organic liquidity growth. WELEPHANT extends this value proposition to the broader DeFi landscape, enabling integrations, yield strategies, and partnerships across chains.
